@Jeffery-Young @mattiaerli97 Since those don't have to do with min/max, it would be better to file separate bugs for them.

@Jeffery-Young Your issue doesn't seem like it would have produced valid CSS in 1.39. If I write `29px + calc(4px/2)`, 1.39.2 produces `29pxcalc(4px/2)`. Producing an error there seems like an improvement over silently producing an invalid value.

@mattiaerli97 I've filed https://github.com/sass/sass/issues/3144 to track that.
